OL,5,
OL,6,CG2010FThe final episode of A Touch of
OL,7,FFrost airs on ITV. Police drama
OL,8,Fstarring Sir David Jason. The show
OL,9,Ffirst aired in 1992.
OL,10,
OL,11,CG2022FA major power failure at ITN's
OL,12,FLondon studios causes production teams
OL,13,Fto temporarily relocate to Leeds to
OL,14,Fbroadcast their news programmes from
OL,15,Fthe studio used by ITV News Calendar.
OL,16,
OL,17,FThe ITV Lunchtime News is presented by
OL,18,FGamal Fahnbulleh. The ITV Evening News
OL,19,Fis presented by Mary Nightingale. News
OL,20,Fat Ten is presented by Tom Bradby.
